{"tid":15090,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一個半月","createTime":"2016-11-30T22:46:06.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-01T04:14:04.000Z","uid":209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"29821e47f4b0aad2726fc0d61fd39844cdc8be3d","tid":15090,"uid":209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T22:46:06.000Z","msg":"多謝你出現一個半月又離我而去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講過好多野 我以為同你會可以有一段長少少既友誼<br />\n同你講過 好多人未深入了解到就會消失<br />\n你個陣話會同我深入了解<br />\n依家諗返真係諷刺 <br />\n你最後都成為左一個會喺我生命中消失既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可能你已經搵到第二個更好更靚既人同佢深入了解啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我只好祝你幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所有所有野真係黎得快，去得快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我真係好唔開心呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9a3da3f786ccb11e038db65c832fd9111fb6a16","tid":15090,"uid":209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T22:49:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f75beebf54a428b50994df493d683d1a61f786d2","tid":15090,"uid":209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T23:18:21.000Z","msg":"無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a0e227b0bf04a9d20833e8625a2b5eb01db140f","tid":15090,"uid":17932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T23:21:10.000Z","msg":"講緊個個咁似我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e38c2516aef417f1b14d56eebbc675e5e136c8c","tid":15090,"uid":42801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-1